<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>일정 목록</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>📅 일정 목록</h1>

<a href="/schedules/new">➕ 새 일정 등록</a>

{{#scheduleList}}
    <hr>
    <div>
        <strong>제목:</strong> {{title}}<br>
        <strong>마감일:</strong> {{dueDate}}<br>
        <strong>완료 여부:</strong> {{#completed}}✅ 완료{{/completed}}{{^completed}}❌ 미완료{{/completed}}<br>

        <a href="/schedules/{{id}}/update">✏️ 수정</a>
        <form action="/schedules/{{id}}/delete" method="post" style="display:inline;">
            <button type="submit">🗑 삭제</button>
        </form>
    </div>
{{/scheduleList}}

{{^scheduleList}}
    <p>등록된 일정이 없습니다.</p>
{{/scheduleList}}
</body>
</html>
